<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$dong-chao-38-43" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/dong-chao-38-43" class="zg-link" title="董超">董超</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhu-hong-kun-52" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhu-hong-kun-52" class="zg-link" title="朱洪堃">朱洪堃</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$liu-cong-39-90" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/liu-cong-39-90" class="zg-link" title="刘聪">刘聪</a></span>
